{"Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil and fill a large bowl with ice water.  In another large bowl, whisk the lime, orange and tomato juices with the tomato paste.  Season with salt, pepper and hot sauce.", "Cook the shrimp in the boiling water just until curled and pink, about 1 minute.  Using a slotted spoon, transfer the shrimp to the ice water.  Return the pot of water to a boil and add the squid.  Cook until firm but tender, about 30 seconds.  Drain immediately and add to the ice water.", 
