{"Preheat oven to 375 degrees.", "Spray a 9 inch pie plate.", "Spread nuts over a baking pan.", "Toast for 7-10 minutes on middle shelf, or until the smell of nuts fills the kitchen.", "Combine oats, flour, remaining pecans, 1/2 teaspoon cinnamon, and a pinch of salt in a food processor.", "Pulse until mixture becomes a coarse meal. Whisk together applesauce and 3 tablespoons maple syrup.", "Mix into dry ingredients to form a soft dough.", "Press mixture into pie plate. Crimp edges. Bake for 10 minutes, and set aside to cool.", 
