{"In a medium-size microwave-safe bowl, stir marmalade with soy sauce. Microwave, uncovered, on high until softened, 1 minute.", "OR melt in a saucepan, stirring often.", "Stir in barbecue sauce.", "Place chicken in crock pot. Pour in sauce. Stir to coat.", "Cover and cook on high setting 4 hours or low 6 hours.", "To bake, preheat oven to 350F {180C}. Place chicken in a large, ovenproof casserole dish that will hold at least 16 cups {4 L}. Pour sauce over chicken. Stir to evenly coat. Set on a baking sheet to catch any drips if it bubbles over.", 
